review: Dr. Lenin was very helpful. He listened to my symptoms with so much patience and gave me meds which helped me recover quickly. Would recommend him to others as well. He also helped me do diagnosis over the to check if I had any other illness which i thought i could have had.Keep up the good work!!

I had a wonderful & warm experience with Dr.Prince from start to finish.
Appreciate Dr. Prince  taking time to go over the diagnosis clearly and treatment options. Very friendly and down to earth and sometimes I felt he is like my younger brother. More than everything he is a great human being .May God bless him

Excellent experience with Dr. Prince, patiently listened to the problem, very friendly,  and caring. Takes time to understand and explain the underlying problem and how it can be prevented.    Never try to rush through the consultation.

The way he explains things is very detailed & easy to understand  for the patient. very genuine and approcable.Thank you
